all five problems, TheBotCompany consistently adopts a flatter
file structure than human submissions, using between one-third
and one-quarter as many files on multi-file problems (P4: 4 vs. 18;
P17: 6 vs. 20), reflecting its tendency to consolidate related logic
rather than decompose into fine-grained modules.
